data.description: Tons of potential in the Center Hall Colonial. Walk in the front door to a spacious first floor. Living room on the right and down the hall is the family room. Galley style kitchen and bathroom off the family room. Garage has been converted to living space and includes a full bath and bedroom. Off the Kitchen is a large deck with pool built in and access to a 4-season spa room with jacuzzi. Basement is mostly finished but has damage. Upstairs is 4 bedrooms a hall bathroom and the primary bedroom has a large on suite bathroom. House has tons of potential but needs a renovation and deep clean.
